0:7:51,7 --> 0:7:56,767
that includes what's shown here in this oblong, the so-called nod box,


131
0:7:56,767 --> 0:8:0,933
a highly conserved motif that's in the DNA


132
0:8:0,933 --> 0:8:6,167
upstream of the nodulation genes, both this set of common nod genes,


